            <thetext>A scenario where you have f.i. a support application depending on calling individuals you need to have one view in a specific language and another view in another language. This is not supported at the moment.

We are proposing to add a locale specific for the widget. That means there is a global locale setting and a widget locale setting.

The translation system needs to check both settings for the string ids. The widget locale should be overriding the global locale.

We will propose an addition with code we are testing right now.</thetext>
